A system built to act before the breach.
With agents that respond in milliseconds.
A control plane that enforces your policies but stays out of your way.
Tooling thatâ€™s fast, explainable, and rooted in technologies we already trust.
The pages ahead outline the how:
â€¢ A high level design that makes action, not just observation, the default
â€¢ A distributed agent model tuned for speed, locality, and autonomy
â€¢ A command architecture that favors transparency and human override
â€¢ Techniques to reduce false positives and increase explainability in the moment, not after
